narratives.question_text: Comments.If you wrote a paper with any of these professors, if the course was taught by more than one professor, or you would like to comment on any aspects previously mentioned
comments: A fun class that touches on various areas of law, history, sociology, anthropology, politics and economics. I found this class to be quite rewarding and it certainly provided much inspiration for further research. The only unfortunate thing was that meeting for only one and a half hours per week didn't allow us to go very deep into each topic.
